OL,3,CBlue Islands suspends operations with
OL,4,Cimmediate effect
OL,6,FAirline Blue Islands has suspended
OL,7,Foperations with immediate effect.
OL,9,FIn a statement, Blue Islands said:
OL,10,F"After 26 years of serving the Channel
OL,11,FIslands, we deeply regret that Blue
OL,12,FIslands has this evening suspended its
OL,13,Foperations.
OL,15,F"After very constructive dialogue with
OL,16,FGovernment of Jersey in recent months,
OL,17,Fincluding what we understood to have
OL,18,Fbeen ongoing assessments of the future
OL,19,Foptions, we were informed this
OL,20,Fafternoon that they are unable to
OL,21,Fprovide further support.
