OL,3,CBlue Islands suspends operations with
OL,4,Cimmediate effect
OL,6,F"This has meant that we now need to
OL,7,Fsuspend flying immediately whilst we
OL,8,Fconsider the options available and how
OL,9,Fwe can help our customers, staff and
OL,10,Fstakeholders."
OL,12,FBlue Islands says anyone who has a
OL,13,Fbooking with them should contact the
OL,14,Fbank or provider of the payment card
OL,15,Fthey used to make the booking.
OL,17,FThey add that anyone who has made a
OL,18,Fbooking through Aurigny for a Blue
OL,19,FIslands flight should contact Aurigny
OL,20,Fdirectly as some of those flights may
OL,21,Fstill be operating.
