OL,6,FPassengers who booked through a travel
OL,7,Fagent or holiday company should
OL,8,Fcontact them for advice and guidance.
OL,10,FSpeculation of the suspension came to
OL,11,Flight earlier today, with ITV News
OL,12,Funderstanding that Jersey's Council of
OL,13,FMinisters have been in talks about the
OL,14,Foperator's future all week.
