OL,6,FIn response to tonight's announcement,
OL,7,FJersey's Treasury Minister, Deputy
OL,8,FElaine Millar, said: "I am saddened by
OL,9,Fthe announcement that Blue Islands has
OL,10,Fsuspended operations, and my immediate
OL,11,Fthoughts are with the people whose
OL,12,Fjobs have been affected and the
OL,13,Fpassengers whose travel will be
OL,14,Fdisrupted.
OL,16,F"For those employees based in Jersey,
OL,17,FGovernment support is ready and
OL,18,Favailable.
