OL,6,F"Air connectivity is vital for our
OL,7,FIsland, and the contingency plans that
OL,8,Fhave been prepared will mean that
OL,9,Fconnections are swiftly reinstated,
OL,10,Fwith priority given to those routes
OL,11,Fmost essential to the provision of
OL,12,Fmedical services. Ports of Jersey are
OL,13,Fproviding advice to people who have
OL,14,Fbeen affected by the flight
OL,15,Fcancellations.
OL,17,F"Anyone who was due to travel with
OL,18,FBlue Islands should not go to the
OL,19,Fairport and should instead rebook with
OL,20,Fan alternative airline.
