OL,6,F"All medical transfer passengers will
OL,7,Fbe supported separately through the
OL,8,FDepartment of Health.
OL,10,F"While Ports of Jersey address the
OL,11,Fshort-term challenges, Government is
OL,12,Fworking with an alternative airline to
OL,13,Fensure that Jersey has reliable and
OL,14,Fsustainable air links for the long
OL,15,Fterm."
OL,17,FThe government loaned the airline #8.5
OL,18,Fmillion during the Covid pandemic and
OL,19,Fhas only been paid back a fraction to
OL,20,Fdate.
