OL,3,CBlue Islands suspends operations with
OL,4,Cimmediate effect
OL,6,FBlue Islands provides key air links
OL,7,Fbetween the Channel Islands and the
OL,8,FUK, as well as a number of other
OL,9,Fdomestic routes and some international
OL,10,Fflights.
OL,12,FIts operations, including some
OL,13,Fseasonal services, cover seven UK
OL,14,Fairports: Bristol, East Midlands,
OL,15,FExeter, Leeds Bradford, Southampton,
OL,16,FNewcastle, Norwich.
OL,18,FIt also runs inter-island flights
OL,19,Fbetween Jersey and Guernsey.
